## Source: ossf-package-analysis (f4edd91c508836997724f9c8be84dd0e437950f7aab6b60ef5f0ee12df9f03e1)
The OpenSSF Package Analysis project identified 'lenskart' @ 1.0.5 (npm) as malicious.

- The package executes one or more commands associated with malicious behavior.
